{"tid":2227811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 運動停滯期我見","createTime":"2020-10-03T05:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T14:26:56.000Z","uid":298386,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"812574d3bfa1ef7672a215c8abf8211e183ae3c6","tid":2227811,"uid":298386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T05:48:02.000Z","msg":"學我偶像攬炒巴咁講 街頭/議會/國際戰線缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">街頭抗爭</span></span><br />\n相信大家都認同一樣野 宜家街頭抗爭既空間真係好有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算最和理非既遊行/集會/築人鏈都唔會做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一日有限聚令 我地呢世都唔會有不反<br />\n甚至無限聚令 港共都唔會批<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">議會抗爭</span></span><br />\n港共已經驚閪 取消選舉 DQ初選勝出參選人<br />\n港共仲諗到新招打散民意內部分化 被委任VS杯葛<br />\n基本上宜家得21個民主派議員 睇唔到有咩出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">國際戰線</span></span><br />\n睇唔少連登POST都講過 議會+街頭 就係比子彈做國際游說<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝手足過往係街頭抗爭既付出 我地引來國安法 引來天下圍攻港共<br />\n 至少 美/英/加/澳/日/印度/歐盟都關注香港問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至少宜家德國肥西都態度轉硬 (我對佢無期望)<br />\n似乎宜家我地唯有等國際有更強硬既野可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講左咁多野 其實我無答案可以點做 諗到的話我就唔洗係到出POST<br />\n但可以拋下磚 大家集思 我相信香港人抗爭創意度係世界之冠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至少白俄/加泰都參考下我地做法 <br />\n1 繼續支持黃色經濟圈 (係好廢 但好多人都會忍唔住食美心/藍店)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2 唔該你地唔好繼續係IG/FB好嬲好嬲好嬲 咁樣只係同溫層打飛機<br />\n唔該你地開Twitter做任務 國際戰線係肯國際戰線做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/twitter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Ftwitter&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmXs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=ffa4207f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/twitter</a><br />\n跟住我就諗唔到 但如果國際戰線重要 再次國際頭條登報點睇? <br />\n<br />\n以下唔該擺係我地生活入面 有時間就做 唔好忘記默默為我地付出既手足<br />\n1. 旁聽師/送車師/遮陣師<br />\n2. 寫信比手足"},{"pid":"3db8a980be56e07e4fc7eda6ef9ad0ba8697d08e","tid":2227811,"uid":298386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T05:50:09.000Z","msg":"自推1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3caddad46041694d8ce3672be964b4f95ad5ea","tid":2227811,"uid":298386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T05:50:19.000Z","msg":"自推2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4260ccee4340220ec6d0879f51465ae4516bdf3","tid":2227811,"uid":298386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T05:50:32.000Z","msg":"自推3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760274197da86c2a02ee7